I still have trouble believing that
Fan-sama is no longer with us...

rows.label: tlk46500171_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I was hoping to break out of my slump
today and get back to carving my
sculpture, but my spirit is still dashed...

rows.label: tlk46500171_03_msg0003
rows.name:
When I'm feeling down, the only
thing that can lift my spirits is a
swig of sweet Odifa.

rows.label: tlk46500171_03_msg0004
rows.name:
You should have some too.
It'll help, I promise.
